Hibernate crud web appplication using MVC pattern, servlet, controller, factory, singleton
DAO,DTO,Connection pool

Tested on java 17 and tomcat 9.0.71

remember to edit src/main/java/in/rahul/util/HibernateUtil.java to put suitable values

keep the table ready or let hibernate create it 

 create table Student (
       sid integer not null auto_increment,
        saddress varchar(255),
        sage integer,
        sname varchar(255),
        primary key (sid)
    );

dependencies:
	servlet-api
	HikariCP
	mysql-connector-j
	slf4j-api
	slf4j-simple
	taglibs-standard-impl
	taglibs-standard-spec
	

